Gregg B wrote a review Jun 2022
1 contribution
Perfect in every way
Definitely book this hotel. I loved my stay and the staff are the best. So friendly and positive, they made my stay really special and made me feel like family. They're great and help in any way they can. The hotel itself is beautiful, different and clean, with everything you need. Kitchenette, great shower, TV, fridge, good air con, and a cool balcony. I loved my stay so much that I booked an extra night and may come back in few days. The location is close to other hotels, bars, restaurants, supermarket and perfect for My Khe beach. It's a short taxi ride from the centre of town but worth it. It's also on a side street so there is little outside traffic noise etc. 11/10 - I wish I could live here
Read more
Date of stay: June 2022
