KereruHugger wrote a review Nov 2019
Wellington, New Zealand81 contributions75 helpful votes
Great location and close to the beach.
Great hotel. Staff were friendly and the room was spacious enough for our family of three. Bikes are free to use and it's close to some great places for dinner!. Although not an issue for us and not a problem with the hotel at all, but more just a note that Da Nang has a LOT of construction going on and this can continue until very late at night and start up again early in the morning so if you are a light sleeper you may want to get a room at the back. Also if you are thinking about going to Sun World please read our review before you go!
Date of stay: October 2019
