Frequently Asked Questions about John Boutique Villa Apartment
Which popular attractions are close to John Boutique Villa Apartment?
Nearby attractions include Malibu Club (0.3 miles), Cheers English Pub (0.2 miles), and Ball and Bee’s Home (0.3 miles).
See all nearby attractions.
What are some of the property amenities at John Boutique Villa Apartment?
Some of the more popular amenities offered include an indoor pool, free wifi, and free breakfast.
See all property amenities.
Which room amenities are available at John Boutique Villa Apartment?
Top room amenities include a kitchenette, a minibar, and air conditioning.
See all room amenities.
What food & drink options are available at John Boutique Villa Apartment?
Guests can enjoy free breakfast and an on-site restaurant during their stay.
Learn more.
Is parking available at John Boutique Villa Apartment?
Yes, free parking is available to guests.
What are some restaurants close to John Boutique Villa Apartment?
Conveniently located restaurants include Horizon Bar, The Eatery, and My Casa Tapas Bar.
See all nearby restaurants.
Are there opportunities to exercise at John Boutique Villa Apartment?
Yes, guests have access to an indoor pool during their stay.
Does John Boutique Villa Apartment have airport transportation?
Yes, John Boutique Villa Apartment offers airport transportation for guests. We recommend calling ahead to confirm details.
